20Court%20in%20September%20had%20asked%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20identify%20all%20religious%20buildings%20in%20the%20State%20which%20would%20include%20churches%2C%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20Sanamahi%20temples%2C%20mosques%20and%20any%20building%20of%20any%20other%20religion%2C%20whether%20existing%20at%20present%20or%20vandalised%2Fdamaged%2Fburnt%20in%20the%20violence%E2%80%9D%20and%20asked%20that%20they%20be%20protected%20from%20encroachment%20and%20destruction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20October%2016%20response%2C%20it%20had%20indicated%20the%20steps%20taken%20in%20this%20regard%20in%20all%20the%2016%20districts.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20further%20submitted%20that%20inspection%20of%20religious%20sites%20could%20not%20be%20completed%20in%20Noney%20and%20Senapati%20districts%20due%20to%20the%20prevailing%20circumstances.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%20its%20latest%20response%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F5-crore-released-for-women-survivors-of-sexual-assault-other-crimes-in-manipur-sc-told%2Farticle67554828.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20identification%20exercise%20had%20been%20completed%20in%20the%20said%20districts%20and%20no%20vandalism%20was%20reported%20in%20Noney%20and%20Senapati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20state%20had%20informed%20the%20apex%20court%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20total%20of%20386%20religious%20institutions%20of%20both%20the%20communities%20have%20suffered%20damage%20subject%20to%20further%20assessment%20which%20is%20on-going%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20200%20lives%20have%20been%20lost%20and%20more%20than%2075%2C000%20persons%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced%20in%20the%20violence%20that%20began%20nearly%20six%20months%20ago%20and%20cont