nnected%20them%20to%20the%20score%20of%20rescuers%20working%20overtime%20to%20bring%20them%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20the%20rescue%20teams%20and%20the%20trapped%20workers%20is%20debris%20about%2040%20metres%20thick.%20Drilling%20through%20this%20and%20bringing%20the%20workers%20home%20has%20been%20a%20tall%20challenge%20owing%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20the%20topography%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20soil%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%203.45%20am%20today%2C%20when%20the%20workers'%20faces%20appeared%20on%20camera%2C%20there%20were%20some%20moments%20of%20excitement%20among%20the%20rescue%20teams.%20The%20mood%20soon%20turned%20serious%20as%20the%20rescuers%20planned%20the%20next%20steps%20in%20their%20daunting%20task.%20They%20assured%20the%20workers%20that%20they%20will%20reach%20them%20soon%20and%20shot%20off%20several%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20alright%3F%20If%20all%20of%20you%20are%20okay%2C%20please%20show%20yourself%20before%20the%20camera.%20Please%20raise%20your%20hands%20and%20smile%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20workers%20were%20told%20over%20the%20walkie-talkie.%20They%20responded%20by%20lining%20up%20before%20the%20camera.%20Their%20faces%20showed%20a%20stubble%20that%20had%20grown%20over%20the%20past%20week%2C%20their%20heads%20were%20covered%20by%20hard%20hats.%20They%20waved%20to%20the%20camera%2C%20signalling%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20reach%20you%20very%20soon%2C%20please%20do%20not%20worry.%20Please%20come%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera%20one%20by%20one.%20We%20want%20to%20show%20your%20relatives%20that%20you%20are%20okay%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20rescuer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20were%20then%20asked%20to%20take%20the%20camera%20from%20inside%20the%20pipe%20and%20focus%20it%20on%20each%20of%20them.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20see%20you%20very%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20rescuer%20said%2C%20asking%20if%20t