ircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20pregnant%20passenger%2C%20whose%20identity%20has%20not%20been%20made%20public%2C%20suddenly%20went%20into%20labour%20aboard%20the%20flight%20while%20the%20crew%20was%20preparing%20for%20takeoff.%C2%A0The%20crew%20responded%20swiftly%20and%20calmly%20handled%20the%20situation.%20Emergency%20services%20and%20paramedics%20at%20the%20Sabiha%20Gokcen%20International%20Airport%20were%20immediately%20called%20in%20to%20assist%20with%20the%20birth.%20The%20woman%20was%C2%A0escorted%20away%20from%20her%20seat%20to%20another%20area%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20where%20the%20paramedics%20helped%20her%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoments%20later%2C%20a%20female%20paramedic%20emerged%20carrying%20the%20baby%2C%20who%20was%20wrapped%20in%20blue%20cloth%2C%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20plane.%C2%A0The%20baby%2C%20who%20was%20born%20prematurely%20and%20did%20not%20make%20any%20noise%2C%20was%20immediately%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20via%20ambulance%20for%20further%20care.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildbirth%20on%20airplanes%20is%20uncommon%20because%20pregnant%20women%20are%20rarely%20allowed%20to%20fly%20in%20their%20third%20trimester.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20baby%20has%20been%20born%20on%20an%20aircraft%20or%20during%20a%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-who-didnt-know-she-was-pregnant-gives-birth-on-plane-report-3603838%5C%22%3Ea%20woman%20passenger%20who%20didn't%20know%20she%20was%20pregnant%20%3C%2Fa%3Egave%20birth%20mid-flight%20after%20going%20to%20the%20bathroom%20with%20a%20stomach%20ache.%20The%20woman%2C%20identified%20as%20Tamara%2C%20was%20on%20a%20KLM%20Royal%20Dutch%20flight%20from%20Guyaquil%2C%20Ecuador%20to%20Amsterdam%20when%20she%20took%20everyone%20in%20the%20aircraft%20by%20surprise%20by%20unexpectedly%20giving%20birth.%20Ms%20Tamara%20was%20flying%20from%20Ecuador%20to%20her%20destination%20in%20Spain%2C%20with%20a%20stop%20at%20Schipol%20Airport%20outside%20Amsterdam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202017%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20''Aviation%2C%20Space%2C%20and%20Environmental%20Medicine%2C''%20the%20odds%20of%20a%20woman%20giving%20birth%20on%20a%20commercial%20flight%20are%20about%201%20in%2032%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Paulo%20Alves%2C%20the%20brand's%20global%20medical%20director%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cntraveler.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-happens-to-babies-born-on-planes%5C%22%3E%20Conde%20Nast%20Traveler%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202018%2C%20''It's%20not%20the%20best%20place%20for%20you%20to%20have%20your%20child%2C%20for%20many%20reasons.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20the%20air%20is%20thinner%2C%20so%20it's%20harder%20for%20the%20baby%20to%20breathe.%20It's%20like%20giving%20birth%20to%20a%20premature%20child%20in%20Mexico%20City%2C%20altitude-wise.''%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700552640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F72lrf6r_baby-born-on-plane_625x300_21_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-gives-birth-on-plane-moments-before-takeoff-onboard-pegasus-flight-to-france-4591690%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20baby%2C%20who%20was%20born%20prematurely%2C%20was%20immediately%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20for%20further%20care.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-gives-birth-on-plane-moments-before-takeoff-onboard-pegasus-flight-to-france-4591690%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-gives-birth-on-plane-moments-before-takeoff-onboard-pegasus-flight-to-france-4591690%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-gives-birth-on-plane-moments-before-takeoff-onboard-pegasus-flight-to-france-4591690%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTuber%20MrBeast%20Spends%207%20Days%20Being%20Buried%20Alive%2C%20Calls%20It%20%26quot%3BMental%20Agony%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPopular%20YouTuber%20MrBeast%20spent%20seven%20days%20inside%20sealed%20inside%20a%20coffin%20and%20buried%20underground%20in%20a%20jaw-dropping%20stunt.%20While%20the%20thought%20of%20being%20buried%20alive%20is%20enough%20to%20send%20shivers%20down%20the%20spines%20of%20most%20people%2C%20MrBeast%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Jimmy%20Donaldson%2C%20spent%20a%20week%20in%20a%20box%20underground%20to%20entertain%20his%20212%20million%20YouTube%20subscribers.%20He%20stated%20that%20the%20stunt%20caused%20him%20%26quot%3Bmental%20agony%26quot%3B%20and%20urged%20his%20followers%20to%20not%20try%20this%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Uma%20Thurman's%20character%20in%20'Kill%20Bill'%2C%20the%20social%20media%20sensation%20opted%20to%20spend%20seven%20days%20underground%20as%20part%20of%20his%20most%20recent%2C%20jaw-dropping%20stunt.%20The%20suit-clad%20celebrity%20was%20initially%20pulled%20down%20into%20the%20ground%20in%20a%20state-of-the-art%20transparent%20coffin%2C%20complete%20with%20food%20and%20water%20to%20begin%20this%20underground%20journey.%20The%20coffin%20also%20had%20cameras%20to%20record%20the%20video%20and%20make%20sure%20nothing%20went%20downhill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7dYTw-jAYkY%3Fsi%3DXo9Zs9GuC3xQ9TJK%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20along%20with%20his%20friends%20used%20an%20excavator%20to%20put%2020%2C000%20pounds%20of%20mud%20on%20top%20of%20the%20coffin%2C%20ensuring%20that%20it%20was%20below%20the%20surface.%20MrBeast%20said%20in%20the%20video%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20entrusting%20my%20life%20to%20this%20coffin%20for%20the%20next%20seven%20days.%26quot%3B%20He%20used%20a%20walkie-talkie%20to%20communicate%20with%20his%20team%20who%20was%20on%20the%20surface.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daredevil%20found%20the%20seven-day%20dirt%20nap%20to%20be%20extremely%20exhausting%20despite%20the%20safety%20precautions.%20Although%20the%20stunt%20was%20voluntary%2C%20he%20broke%20down%20in%20tears%20on%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20including%20when%20he%20was%20being%20taken%20out%20of%20the%20casket.%20Another%20worry%20was%20that%20after%20spending%20so%20much%20time%20in%20a%20small%20area%2C%20he%20would%20get%20blood%20clots%20in%20his%20legs%20and%20would%20be%20unable%20to%20stand.%20Fortunately%2C%20he%20survived%20his%20brief%20internment%20without%20experiencing%20any%20injury.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20attempted%20a%20similar%20record%20for%20being%20buried%20alive%20for%2050%20hours%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20MrBeast%20earned%20%2454%20million%20in%202021.%20He%20reportedly%20makes%20around%20%245%20million%20a%20month%2C%20making%20him%20YouTube's%20highest-paid%20content%20creator%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20active%20on%20YouTube%20since%202012%2C%20MrBeast%20just%20became%20well-known%20in%202018%20after%20giving%20thousands%20of%20cash%20to%20obscure%20Twitch%20streamers%20and%20YouTubers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700552460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fd1rlh9eg_mrbeast_625x300_21_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fyoutuber-mrbeast-spends-7-days-being-buried-alive-calls-it-mental-agony-4591759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20the%20stunt%20was%20voluntary%2C%20he%20broke%20down%20in%20tears%20on%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20including%20when%20he%20was%20being%20taken%20out%20of%20the%20casket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fyoutuber-mrbeast-spends-7-days-being-buried-alive-calls-it-mental-agony-4591759%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fyoutuber-mrbeast-spends-7-days-being-buried-alive-calls-it-mental-agony-4591759%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fyoutuber-mrbeast-spends-7-days-being-buried-alive-calls-it-mental-agony-4591759%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Take%20Us%20For%20Granted%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court's%20Tough%20Words%20For%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20hard%20on%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi%20governments%20Tuesday%20-%20and%20offered%20a%20measure%20of%20support%20to%20farmers%20from%20the%20former%20state%20-%20as%20it%20continues%20a%20marathon%20hearing%20into%20a%20clutch%20of%20petitions%20about%20the%20toxic%20air%20that%20blankets%20and%20chokes%20the%20national%20capital%20every%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20SK%20Kaul%20and%20S%20Dhulia%20ordered%20the%20states%20-%20both%20ruled%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20-%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20burning%20of%20agricultural%20waste%2C%20which%20adds%20significantly%20to%20Delhi's%20AQI%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20most%20polluted%20November%20in%20six%20years...%20the%20problem%20is%20known%20(and)%20it%20is%20your%20job%20to%20control%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20told%20the%20two%20states%2C%20and%20neighbouring%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20reprimanded%20the%20Delhi%20government%20over%20delayed%20funding%20of%20the%20Delhi-Meerut%20RRTS%20(regional%20rapid%20transport%20system)%20and%20ordered%20funds%20be%20transferred%20from%20the%20AAP's%20spending%20on%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20not%20complied%20with%20our%20order.%20We%20don't%20have%20any%20other%20way.%20You%20can't%20take%20us%20for%20granted...%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20court%20rebuked%20the%20Delhi%20government%20after%20it%20said%20it%20could%20not%20contribute%20to%20a%20rail%20network%20that%20will%20connect%20the%20city%20to%20neighbouring%20states%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20reduce%20vehicular%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20had%20expressed%20its%20inability%20to%20provide%20its%20share%20of%20funds%20-%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20415%20crore%20-%20after%20which%20the%20court%20directed%20it%20to%20place%20on%20record%20funds%20spent%20on%20ads%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20order%20was%20stayed%20for%20a%20week.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Delhi%20government%20doesn't%20pay%20the%20RRTS%20amount%20within%20a%20week%2C%20the%20funds%20will%20be%20transferred%20from%20its%20'advertisements'%20allocations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20warned%20the%20ruling%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%2C%20however%2C%20more%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20condition%20of%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%2C%20who%20have%20come%20under%20severe%20scrutiny%20(again)%20for%20burning%20agricultural%20or%20crop%20waste%2C%20or%20stubble.%20%26quot%3BThe%20farmer%20is%20being%20made%20a%20villain...%20and%20he%20is%20not%20being%20heard%20from.%20He%20must%20have%20some%20reason%20to%20burn%20this%20stubble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20farmers%20-%20who%20have%20been%20accused%20by%20all%20sides%20of%20contributing%20to%20the%20air%20quality%20crisis%20-%20have%20not%20been%20represented%20in%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20suggested%20the%20Punjab%20government%20offer%20farmers%20incentives%20to%20not%20burn%20stubble.%20%26quot%3BThey%20should%20learn%20from%20Haryana%20regarding%20incentives%20given%20to%20farmers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20people%20who%20are%20burning%20the%20stubble%20will%20not%20come%20here%20(they%20are%20not%20represented%20here).%20We%20understand%20that%20those%20who%20have%20substantial%20land%20holdings%20will%20not%20come%20here%20(to%20the%20court%2C%20because%20they%20can%20afford%20the%20machinery%20to%20safely%20dispose%20farm%20waste)...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20people%20with%20small%20land%20holdings%20are%20struggling%20with%20stubble%20burning.%20For%20poor%20farmers%2C%20the%20state%20should%20fund%20100%20per%20cent%20of%20machinery...%20this%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20told%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20the%20government%20can%20take%20the%20product%20and%20sell%20it...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20winter%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20Delhi%20and%20surrounding%20regions%20plunges%20to%20extremely%20toxic%20levels%2C%20triggering%20widespread%20health%20scares%20and%20forcing%20schools%20and%20colleges%20to%20shut%20down%20for%20days.%20This%20morning%20the%20AQI%20was%20at%20323%2C%20indicating%20'very%20poor'%20air%20quality%2C%20central%20government%20data%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20various%20factors%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20hazardous%20air%20covering%20Delhi%20at%20this%20time%20of%20the%20year%2C%20including%20farm%20fires%2C%20fireworks%20during%20Diwali%2C%20vehicular%20traffic%20and%20dust%20from%20construction%20activities%2C%20all%20of%20which%20hangs%20over%20the%20city%20because%20there%20is%20no%20wind%20to%20disperse%20the%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Punjab%20reported%20634%20farm%20fires%20in%20a%20day%20as%20many%20farmers%20continue%20to%20set%20paddy%20crop%20waste%20on%20fire%20-%20so%20they%20can%20ready%20the%20field%20for%20a%20quick%20second%20crop%20-%20despite%20police%20warnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700552400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Foa4fnap_stubble-burni