ibers%2C%20exits%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20old%20subscribers%20%E2%80%93%20rose%20by%2014.9%25%20to%201.72%20million%20in%20September%2C%20these%20numbers%20are%20provisional%20and%20are%20usually%20subject%20to%20significant%20revisions%20in%20the%20following%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20women%20among%20the%20fresh%20EPF%20subscribers%20in%20September%20declined%20from%2026.12%25%20in%20August%20to%2025.3%25%20(226%2C392).%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20share%20of%20individuals%20in%20the%2018-28%20age%20group%20increased%20slightly%20from%2067.93%25%20in%20August%20to%2068.8%25%20in%20September.%20The%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20this%20age%20group%20is%20a%20crucial%20metric%20as%20these%20individuals%20are%20%E2%80%9Cusually%20first-timers%20in%20the%20labour%20market%2C%20thus%20reflecting%20its%20robustness%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20labour%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20around%2041.46%25%20of%20the%20net%20membership%20addition%20in%20September%20came%20from%20expert%20services%2C%20including%20manpower%20suppliers%2C%20normal%20contractors%2C%20security%20services%2C%20and%20miscellaneous%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20month-on-month%20comparison%20of%20industry-wise%20data%20displays%20significant%20growth%20in%20the%20members%20working%20in%20establishments%20engaged%20in%20the%20sugar%20industry%2C%20courier%20services%2C%20iron%20and%20steel%2C%20hospitals%2C%20travel%20agencies%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%2C%20however%2C%20reported%20positive%20trends%20in%20the%20labour%20markets%20for%20September.%20The%20unemployment%20rate%20dropped%20to%20a%20one-year%20low%2C%20decreasing%20from%208.10%25%20in%20August%20to%207.09%25%20in%20September.%20Notably%2C%20rural%20unemployment%20fell%20to%206.20%25%20from%207.11%25%20in%20August%2C