ecurity%20prison%20for%20offenders%20who%20have%20been%20given%20lengthy%20sentences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChong%20testified%20that%20Kobi%20had%20promised%20to%20help%20him%20get%20a%20transfer%20out%20of%20A1%20in%20return%20for%20lending%20or%20giving%20Kobi%20the%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChong%20said%20he%20knew%20that%20Kobi%20did%20not%20have%20the%20capability%20or%20authority%20to%20help%20transfer%20him%20out%20of%20A1.%20However%2C%20Kobi%20said%20he%20had%20a%20friend%20who%20was%20an%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20who%20could%20help%20Chong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKobi%20got%20a%20friend%20to%20see%20Chong%2C%20but%20the%20latter%20was%20still%20not%20transferred%20after%20a%20medical%20review%20in%20early%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20rejected%20Kobi%20when%20the%20prison%20officer%20asked%20him%20to%20get%20his%20friends%20or%20family%20to%20pass%20him%20money%2C%20and%20complained%20that%20he%20had%20not%20been%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20defence%2C%20Kobi%20denied%20asking%20for%20money%20from%20Chong%20on%20any%20of%20the%20eight%20occasions.%20He%20claimed%20that%20he%20spoke%20to%20Chong%20only%20during%20yard%20time%2C%20when%20there%20were%20always%20inmates%20within%20hearing%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKobi%20alleged%20that%20Chong%20had%20lied%20in%20order%20to%20be%20transferred%20out%20of%20A1.%20When%20an%20allegation%20is%20made%20against%20a%20prison%20officer%2C%20either%20the%20officer%20or%20the%20inmate%20will%20be%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChong%20had%20written%20down%20details%20on%20a%20magazine%20in%20his%20cell%20whenever%20Kobi%20asked%20him%20for%20money.%20When%20he%20received%20a%20new%20magazine%2C%20he%20would%20copy%20over%20his%20records%20before%20discarding%20the%20old%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202016%2C%20before%20going%20to%20stay%20at%20Changi%20Medical%20Centre%2C%20Chong%20copied%20over%20his%20latest%20version%20of%20records%20from%20paper%20he%20tore%20from%20a%20novel%