%20against%20the%20watchdog.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%20and%20Kirsty%20Wigglesworth%20-%20WPA%20Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMedia%20Matters%20was%20served%20a%20double%20whammy%20on%20Monday%2C%20after%20reporting%20on%20X's%20advertising%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20said%20X%20placed%20ads%20next%20to%20pro-Nazi%20content%20%E2%80%94%20leading%20to%20an%20advertiser%20exodus%20from%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20now%20suing%20the%20watchdog%2C%20and%20Texas%20AG%20Ken%20Paxton%20is%20investigating%20the%20group%20for%20fraud.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%20Attorney%20General%20Ken%20Paxton%20on%20Monday%20launched%20a%20fraud%20investigation%20into%20Media%20Matters%20for%20America%2C%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20non-profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20actions%2C%20announced%20on%20Monday%2C%20form%20a%20double%20whammy%20for%20Media%20Matters%20that%20hinges%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediamatters.org%2Ftwitter%2Fmusk-endorses-antisemitic-conspiracy-theory-x-has-been-placing-ads-apple-bravo-ibm-oracle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Musk's%20X%20was%20placing%20ads%20next%20to%20pro-Nazi%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20published%20Thursday%2C%20triggered%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvertisers-reaction-elon-musk-endorsing-antisemitic-post-x-employees-report-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20exodus%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20X%2C%20after%20which%20Musk%20declared%20that%20he'd%20file%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-thermonuclear-lawsuit-against-media-watchdog-that-exposed-nazi-linked-ads-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bthermonuclear%26quot%3B%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Media%20Matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20alleged%20that%20Media%20Matters%20manipulated%20its%20findings%20by%20deliberately%20following%20only%20a%20small%20selection%20of%20extremist%20accounts%20and%20big%20advertisers%2C%20then%20cherry-picking%20instances%20when%20posts%20from%20both%20categories%20were%20next%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20Paxton%20is%20jumping%20into%20the%20fray%20as%20well%2C%20with%20his%20office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.texasattorneygeneral.gov%2Fnews%2Freleases%2Fattorney-general-ken-paxton-opens-investigation-media-matters-potential-fraudulent-activity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaying%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20troubled%26quot%3B%20by%20Musk's%20allegations.%20His%20statement%20called%20Media%20Matters%20a%20%26quot%3Bradical%20anti-free%20speech%20organization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20examining%20the%20issue%20closely%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20public%20has%20not%20been%20deceived%20by%20the%20schemes%20of%20radical%20left-wing%20organizations%20who%20would%20like%20nothing%20more%20than%20to%20limit%20freedom%20by%20reducing%20participation%20in%20the%20public%20square%2C%26quot%3B%20Paxton%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Musk's%20part%2C%20the%20billionaire's%20X%20Corp%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20in%20Texas%20alleging%20that%20Media%20Matters%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20smear%20campaign%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20social%20media%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20accuses%20Media%20Matters%20of%20%26quot%3Bendlessly%20scrolling%20and%20refreshing%20its%20unrepresentative%2C%20hand-selected%20feed%26quot%3B%20to%20generate%20its%20report%2C%20which%20was%20released%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watchdog's%20analysis%20had%20shown%20examples%20of%20ads%20from%20five%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20IBM%2C%20Oracle%2C%20Xfinity%2C%20Bravo%2C%20and%20Apple%20%E2%80%94%20next%20to%20antisemitic%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20X's%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20no%20%26quot%3Bauthentic%26quot%3B%20users%20on%20X%20saw%20the%20combination%20of%20ads%20and%20pro-Nazi%20content%20that%20Media%20Matters%20found%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20one%20other%20user%20who%20saw%20Apple's%20ad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20calls%20for%20Media%20Matters%20to%20take%20down%20its%20report%20and%20asks%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20amount%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20Media%20Matters%20President%20Angelo%20Carusone%20said%20X's%20lawsuit%20was%20%26quot%3Bfrivolous%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmeant%20to%20bully%20X's%20critics%20into%20silence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMedia%20Matters%20stands%20behind%20its%20reporting%20and%20looks%20forward%20to%20winning%20in%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20Carusone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Media%20Matters%20representative%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20when%20asked%20to%20comment%20on%20Paxton's%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Paxton%2C%20a%20staunch%20conservative%2C%20has%20investigated%20a%20party%20that%20Musk%20also%20took%20issue%20with.%20In%20June%202022%2C%20the%20attorney%20general%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.texasattorneygeneral.gov%2Fnews%2Freleases%2Fag-paxton-launches-investigation-against-twitter-potentially-deceiving-texas-consumers-texas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20a%20probe%20into%20Twitter%2C%20now%20called%20X%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20whether%20it%20falsified%20reports%20on%20bot%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2022%2Fmay%2F17%2Felon-musk-twitter-deal-bot-tesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20as%20Musk%20had%20raised%20questions%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%20bot%20accounts%20while%20in%20talks%20to%20buy%20Twitter%20for%20%2444%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaxton's%20office%20has%20not%20announced%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20bot%20