0Are%20on%20Ceasefire%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28154925%2Fimage-1445.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20expect%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20in%20the%20next%20%E2%80%98several%20days%E2%80%99.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dr.%20Musa%20Abu%20Marzouq%2C%20the%20head%20of%20international%20relations%20of%20Hamas%2C%20speaking%20from%20Doha%2C%20disclosed%20that%20there%20could%20be%20a%20ceasefire%20for%205%20days%20accompanied%20with%20an%20an%20exchange%20of%20hostages%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Israel%20is%20considering%20stopping%20its%20assault%20on%20Gaza%20for%205%20days.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20Hamas%20will%20probably%20release%2050%20Israelis%20who%20were%20taken%20hostage%20by%20its%20fighters%20in%20their%20attack%20October%207%20attack%20and%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20Israel%20may%20release%20some%20Palestinians%20in%20its%20prisons.%20It%20was%20not%20clear%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20whether%20Israel%20is%20ready%20to%20release%20some%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20%E2%80%93%20held%20in%20its%20prisons%20for%20years%20%E2%80%93%20in%20exchange%20for%20these%20hostages%20which%20include%20147%20children.%20If%20the%20condition%20of%20Hamas%20is%20fulfilled%2C%20the%20ill-fated%20Palestinians%20held%20illegally%20by%20Israel%20can%20feel%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20note%20that%20the%20very%20world%20which%20is%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Israeli%20hostages%20never%20felt%20it%20necessary%20to%20ask%20Israel%20to%20release%20the%20Palestinians%20it%20keeps%20capturing%20and%20imprisoning%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20an%20interesting%20irony%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Israeli%20jails%20are%20considered%20arrests%20and%20legal%20in%20a%20way%2C%20but%20the%20Israelis%20who%20are%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20Hamas%20are%20called%20hostages%2C%20which%20has%20no%20legal%20sanction.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20against%20Hamas.%20It%20considers%20this%20act%20unacceptable%20but%20thinks%20Israel%20has%20a%20right%20to%20arrest%20Palestinians.%20So%20there%20is%20international%20pressure%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Israelis%20but%20the%20freedom%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20for%20the%20international%20community.%20They%20are%20destined%20to%20languish%20in%20the%20Israeli%20jails%2C%20unheard%20and%20unseen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1-300x158.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1-1024x538.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681946%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Jewish%20protester%20in%20a%20pro-Palestine%20demonstration%20in%20the%20US.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40jvplive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20Hamas%20is%20raising%20its%20voice%20for%20their%20release.%20But%20its%20words%20are%20considered%20offensive%20since%20it%20has%20been%20declared%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20international%20community.%20But%20if%20no%20one%20else%20speaks%20for%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20then%20should%20the%20Palestinians%20not%20listen%20to%20Hamas%20just%20because%20it%20has%20been%20declared%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20powerful%20of%20the%20world%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20yet%20clear%20whether%20the%20Palestinians%20will%20be%20released%20or%20not.%20Then%20why%20is%20Hamas%20ready%20for%20this%20ceasefire%3F%20Because%20it%20is%20important%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20to%20survive.%20It%20is%20necessary%20for%20them%20to%20get%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20access%20to%20internet.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20treat%20the%20injured%20Palestinians%20left%20behind%20among%20the%2013%2C000%20that%20are%20dead.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20people%20to%20get%20food%20and%20water.%20Every%20minute%20of%20absence%20of%20firing%20or%20bombing%20means%20a%20life%20saved%2C%20a%20limb%20still%20attached%20to%20the%20body%20it%20belongs%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20governments%20of%20the%20power%20wielding%20world%20would%20not%20allow%20it%20as%20they%20have%20closed%20ranks%20behind%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegation%20against%20Hamas%20is%20that%20it%20was%20not%20concerned%20about%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%20Why%20else%20would%20it%20have%20attacked%20Israel%20on%20October%207%3F%20Did%20it%20not%20know%20how%20Israel%20would%20react%3F%20I%20found%20this%20question%20very%20interesting.%20Implicit%20in%20this%20question%20is%20the%20assumption%20that%20Israel%20is%20a%20bully%20and%20you%20should%20not%20do%20anything%20even%20if%20it%20is%20beating%20you%20daily%2C%20looting%20your%20houses%20and%20land.%20And%20that%20you%20do%20not%20expect%20a%20measured%20response%20from%20it%20to%20any%20crisis.%20That%20it%20would%20indiscriminately%20wreak%20vengeance%20on%20everyone%20it%20thinks%20Hamas%20represents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20if%20Hamas%20is%20ready%20to%20go%20the%20extra%20mile%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%2C%20then%20the%20reason%20behind%20this%20decision%20is%20its%20concern%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F685321%2Fpalestine-palestinians-and-the-western-liberals-burden%2F%5C%22%3EPalestine%2C%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Western%20Liberal%E2%80%99s%20Burden%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20just%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20not%20only%20Israel%2C%20but%20also%20the%20governments%20of%20its%20patron%20states%20like%20the%20US%2C%20England%2C%20Canada%20and%20Germany%20were%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20stopping%20violence%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%20Why%20are%20they%20now%20eager%20for%20it%3F%20They%20were%20after%20all%20not%20averse%20to%20killing%20children%2C%20attacking%20hospitals%20and%20UN%20facilities%2C%20destroying%20Gaza.%20Remember%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20callous%20response%C2%A0%20to%20the%20question%20about%20ceasefire%3F%20He%20had%20smugly%20responded%20%3A%20%E2%80%98No.%20Not%20possible.%E2%80%99%20So%20what%20has%20changed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20decision%20of%20ceasefire%20is%20taken%2C%20then%20its%20credit%20belongs%20to%20the%20American%20and%20European%20youth%20that%20has%20not%20left%20the%20streets%20since%20the%20Israeli%20attack%20and%20have%20continued%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20their%20governments%20to%20ask%20Israel%20to%20go%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20Lakhs%20of%20youngsters%20%E2%80%93%20in%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Toronto%20and%20Berlin%2C%20and%20scores%20of%20other%20big%20and%20small%20cities%20across%20the%20US%20and%20other%20wester%20countries%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20carrying%20Palestinian%20flags%2C%20have%20been%20demonstrating%20against%20the%20Israeli%20attack.%20They%20are%20blocking%20railway%20stations%2C%20bridges%2C%20and%20intersections.%20Protesters%20took%20over%20the%20stage%20of%20a%20Democratic%20Party%20convention%20in%20the%20USA.%20They%20are%20protesting%20against%20t