%20Protest%20Decade%20and%20the%20Missing%20Revolution%2C%E2%80%99%20Vincent%20Bevins%2C%20Public%20Affairs%2C%20an%20imprint%20of%20Hachette%2C%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20is%20our%20immediate%20past%2C%20the%20intense%20street%20protests%20we%20have%20witnessed%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20in%20this%20millennium%2C%20be%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98Arab%20Spring%E2%80%99%2C%20protests%20in%20Chile%2C%20Spain%2C%20Sudan%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Greece%20or%20Occupy%20Wall%20Street%2C%20which%20remain%20a%20black%20box.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20few%20attempts%20to%20look%20at%20the%20full%20spectrum%20of%20protests%20unfolding%20across%20continents.%20Though%20studies%2C%20among%20others%2C%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Power%20of%20the%20Street%3A%20Evidence%20from%20Egypt%E2%80%99s%20Arab%20Spring%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Daron%20Acemoglu%2C%20Tarek%20A.%20Hassan%20and%20Ahmed%20Tahoun%20and%20Zeynep%20Tufekci%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%20and%20Tear%20Gas%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Power%20and%20Fragility%20of%20Networked%20Protest%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20highly%20informative%20accounts%20but%20studies%20are%20often%20focussed%20on%20one%2C%20not%20looking%20at%20the%20many%20demonstrations%20that%20simultaneously%20burst%20forth%20between%202010%20and%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJournalist%20and%20author%20Vincent%20Bevins%2C%20in%20his%20landmark%20new%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20If%20We%20Burn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20manages%20to%20draw%20our%20attention%20to%20street%20mobilisations%20which%20left%20us%20energised%20and%20exhausted%2C%20but%20also%20left%20a%20revolution-sized%20hole%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheorists%20and%20chroniclers%20who%20followed%20the%20%E2%80%98movements%E2%80%99%20with%20interest%20and%20hope%20of%20course%20would%20have%20noticed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%20revolution%E2%80%9D%20left%20behind%20in%20the%20aftermath.%20But%20Bevins%20finds%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%20revolution%E2%80%9D%20reason%20enough%20to%20go%20behind%20the%20fizz%20and%20the%20fury%20and%20ask%20difficult%20questions%20about%20why%20so%20little%20changed%2C%20if%20there%20was%20so%20much%20fervour%2C%20heat%20and%20noise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStarting%20in%20the%20period%20after%20World%20War%20II%20and%20the%20decolonisation%20that%20followed%2C%20Bevins%20focusses%20on%20new%20means%20of%20communication%20that%20offered%20a%20new%20way%20of%20articulating%20politics%2C%20they%20were%20careful%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98old%20left%E2%80%99%2C%20proud%20to%20call%20themselves%20the%20%E2%80%98new%20Left%E2%80%99.%20This%20was%20seen%20as%20horizontalist%2C%20non-hierarchical%20and%20more%20representative.%20This%20was%20a%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20what%20they%20saw%20as%20the%20old%20way%20of%20trying%20to%20usher%20in%20revolutions%20and%20change.%20A%20mix%20of%20the%20use%20of%20news%20media%2C%20staging%20demonstrations%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20city%2C%20getting%20together%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20pamphlets%20and%20allowing%20those%20gathered%20to%20work%20their%20magic%20%E2%80%93%20rather%20than%20think%20through%20change%20with%20a%20vanguard%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20rallying%20masses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBevins%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20says%20at%20the%20outset%20that%20he%20is%20not%20a%20historian.%20But%20having%20%E2%80%9Ccarried%20out%20over%20two%20hundred%20interviews%20in%20twelve%20countries%2C%20speaking%20with%20the%20people%20who%20created%20the%20street%20movements%2C%20many%20of%20the%20politicians%20who%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20them%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20people%20whose%20lives%20were%20affected%E2%80%9D%20gives%20him%20considerable%20command%20over%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%20He%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9Cour%20conversations%20varied%20widely%2C%20but%20I%20attempted%20to%20orient%20them%20all%20around%20a%20few%20apparently%20naive%2C%20almost%20intentionally%20stupid%20questions%3A%20What%20led%20to%20the%20protest%20explosion%3F%20What%20were%20its%20goals%3F%20Were%20they%20achieved%3F%20If%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20achieved%2C%20why%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Finterview-soumyabrata-choudhury-on-our-capacity-for-philosophy-protests-and-isolation%5C%22%3EInterview%3A%20On%20Our%20Capacity%20for%20Philosophy%2C%20Protests%20and%20Isolation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20acknowledges%20his%20debt%20to%20the%20frameworks%20of%201789%20and%201917%20which%20%E2%80%9Chave%20served%20as%20reference%20points%20for%20so%20much%20revolutionary%20practice%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20trace%20the%20ways%20that%20intellectual%20history%20on%20the%20left%20has%20shaped%20contemporary%20protest%2C%20even%20if%20the%20desires%20expressed%20in%20recent%20episodes%20have%20fallen%20all%20over%20the%20political%20spectrum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20throws%20up%20enough%20for%20readers%20to%20attempt%20an%20answer%20to%20the%20central%20question%20of%20why%20these%20eruptions%20on%20the%20street%20often%20had%20exactly%20the%20opposite%20effect%20as%20that%20intended%20by%20those%20at%20the%20barricades.%20Ask%20any%20tourist%20trying%20to%20look%20for%20the%20remains%20of%20Tahrir%20Square%20in%20Cairo%20or%20those%20making%20enquiries%20of%20the%20fruit%20seller%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20on%20in%20Tunisia%2C%20whose%20immolation%20led%20to%20events%20that%20spread%20like%20wildfire%20across%20the%20region.%20The%20Arab%20Spring%20was%20anything%20but%2C%20in%20hindsight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20central%20debate%20remains%20that%20of%20how%20much%20spontaneity%20and%20horizontalism%20can%20stand-in%20for%20discipline%2C%20pre-planning%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20is%20to%20follow%20after%20the%20fall%20(should%20a%20fall%20be%20effected%2C%20in%20the%20first%20place).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20We%20Burn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20achieves%20its%20very%20difficult%20aim%20%E2%80%93%20quite%20like%20what%20Naomi%20Klein%E2%80%99s%20landmark%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20Logo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20did%20as%20the%20last%20millennium%20closed%20%E2%80%93%20of%20getting%20a%20grip%20over%20events%20spread%20across%20the%20globe%20with%20solid%20reportage.%20Like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20Logo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20offered%20a%20brush%20with%20the%20disconcerting%20truth%20of%20what%20was%20happening%20with%20labour%20and%20big%20capital%20as%20the%20new%20economic%20order%20was%20turning%20into%20a%20global%20beast%20in%20the%20nineties%2C%20this%20book%20is%20essential%20reading.%20It%20has%20a%20reporter%E2%80%99s%20attention%20to%20detail%20as%20events%20were%20unfolding%2C%20combined%20with%20reflections%20from%20several%20protagonists%2C%20makers%20of%20movements%20and%20those%20impacted%2C%20people%20the%20author%20spoke%20to%2C%20long%20after%20the%20tide%20had%20subsided.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDisappointingly%2C%20India%20is%20excluded%20from%20the%20ambit%20of%20research%2C%20despite%20having%20experienced%20its%20own%20share%20of%20significant%20street%20turmoil%20over%20%E2%80%98corruption%E2%80%99%20in%202011%20and%20then%20in%202019-20%20over%20questions%20of%20citizenship%2C%20then%20over%20the%20food%20economy.%20But%20the%20instances%20studied%20here%20offer%20many%20parallels%20to%20our%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20case%20that%20even%20in%202023%2C%20we%20are%20too%20close%20to%20the%20slogans%20and%20the%20marches%20on%20the%20street%20to%20be%20able%20to%20judge%20what%20has%20only%20just%20gone%20by.%20Many%20would%20say%2C%20it%20is%20anything%20but%20over%2C%20eg.%2C%201800%20A.D.%20would%20not%20have%20been%20the%20best%20time%20to%20pass%20judgement%20on%20what%20events%20at%20the%20Bastille%20in%201789%20were%20to%20mean%20for%20the%20world.%20Perhaps%20more%20time%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20go%20by%20before%20we%20judge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20We%20Burn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20more%20than%20a%20first%20draft%20of%20history.%20It%20offers%20unsettling%20propositions%20about%20the%20present%20we%20find%20ourselves%20in%2C%20and%20the%20prospects%20for%20change%2C%20and%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700534701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21075956%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fmass-protest-decade-vincent-bevins-book-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20'missing%20revolution'%20is%20reason%20enough%20to%20interrogate%20the%20fizz%20and%20the%20fury%20behind%20people%20pouring%20onto%20the%20streets.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20ask%20some%20tough%20questions%20about%20why%20so%20little%20changed%2C%20if%20there%20was%20so%20much%20heat%20and%20noise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fmass-protest-decade-vincent-bevins-book-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Plastic%20Rice%E2%80%99%3A%20Why%20the%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Experiment%20With%20an%20Artificial%20Grain%20is%20Hard%20to%20Swallow%20for%20Rural%20Adivasis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21103802%2FIllustration-Anumeha-1200x600-1.jpg%5C%