ars%20the%20soil%20has%20turned%20more%20acidic.%20Many%20farmers%20now%20rely%20on%20hybrid%20seeds%20varieties%2C%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9CMDU1010%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CIR64%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CPH76%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20use%20fertilisers%20to%20grow%20paddy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21064956%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-6.47.46.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21064956%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-6.47.46.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21064956%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-6.47.46-300x191.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21064956%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-6.47.46-1024x650.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22762%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESinghbhum%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20grow%20hundreds%20of%20nutritious%20folk%20varieties%20of%20rice%2C%20but%20over%20the%20years%2C%20they%20have%20switched%20to%20cultivating%20other%20varieties.%C2%A0Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20new%20strategy%20to%20combat%20anaemia%20and%20malnutrition%2C%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20October%202021%2C%20it%20began%20supplying%20new%20kind%20of%20rice%2C%20chemically%20fortified%20with%20iron%2C%20vitamin%20B12%20and%20folic%20acid%2C%20to%20the%20poor%20here%2C%20including%20small%20farmers%20such%20as%20Kamal%20Kant%20Gope%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Panajea%20village.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndustrial%20processing%2C%20and%20abrasive%20polishing%20to%20increase%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwhiteness%E2%80%9D%20of%20rice%20strips%20the%20grain%20of%20its%20bran%20layer%2C%20a%20dietary%20fibre%20rich%20in%20minerals%20and%20other%20nutrients.%20As%20rice%20grains%20get%20stripped%20of%20nutrients%2C%20some%20development%20experts%20advocate%20re-introducing%20nutrients%20into%20rice%2C%20by%20fortifying%20it%20with%20a%20micronutrient%20premix.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20policy%20called%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20scale%20fortification%E2%80%9D%2C%20micro-nutrients%20are%20artificially%20added%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3Estaples%2C%20such%20as%20rice.%20How%20it%20is%20being%20done%20in%20rice%20is%20this%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dried%20powder%20%E2%80%9Cpre-mix%E2%80%9D%20of%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20%E2%80%93%20iron%2C%20vitamin%20B12%2C%20folic%20acid%20%E2%80%93%20is%20added%20into%20broken%20rice%2C%20or%20powdered%20rice%20grains.%20The%20paste%2C%20containing%20factory-made%20nutrients%2C%20is%20passed%20through%20pasta-extrusion%20equipment%20to%20manufacture%20new%20grains%2C%20with%20a%20slightly%20artificial%20appearance%20compared%20to%20natural%20rice.%20The%20new%20grains%20are%20mixed%20into%20regular%20rice%20supplied%20to%20the%20poor%20monthly%20in%20gunny%20bags%20as%20a%20food%20subsidy%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDalbhumgarh%20and%20Chakulia%20blocks%20were%20among%20the%20sites%20in%20a%20national%20pilot%20study%20for%20this%20mandatory%20rice%20fortification%20scheme%2C%20chosen%20because%20most%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20rice%20mills%20are%20located%20here%2C%20and%20also%20because%20of%20the%20history%20and%20trend%20of%20paddy%20production%20here.%20It%20has%20now%20been%20many%20months%20since%20Gope%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Dalbhumgarh%2C%20first%20held%20a%20new%20opaque%20rice%20grain%20made%20in%20an%20industrial%20unit%20in%20his%20palm%2C%20instead%20of%20translucent%20grains%20that%20ripen%20every%20year%20in%20the%20emerald%20stalks%20in%20his%20fields.%20He%20remained%20sceptical%20of%20what%20the%20government%20was%20providing%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfood%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20pressures%20us%20to%20eat%20it%20saying%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9CVitamin%20Rice%E2%80%9D%2C%20at%20least%20it%20ought%20to%20have%20some%20taste%20or%20the%20qualities%20of%20rice%3F%E2%80%9D%20Gope%20asked.%20He%20explained%20with%20some%20exasperation%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20rice.%20If%20I%20hold%20it%20tight%20in%20my%20fist%2C%20it%20falls%20away%20like%20a%20grain%20of%20sand%2C%20it%20does%20not%20stick%20like%20rice.%20Even%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emaarh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(the%20water%20left%20after%20rice%20is%20cooked)%20is%20of%20very%20thin%20consistency.%20Then%20how%20can%20it%20be%20nutritious%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065143%2F2-natural-versus-fortified-grains-on-mat.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065143%2F2-natural-versus-fortified-grains-on-mat.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065143%2F2-natural-versus-fortified-grains-on-mat-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065143%2F2-natural-versus-fortified-grains-on-mat-1024x769.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20fortified%20rice%20made%20using%20extrusion%20machine%20in%20a%20factory%20have%20an%20artificial%20appearance%20compared%20to%20natural%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGope%20said%20that%20those%20who%20cultivate%20rice%20such%20as%20him%20know%20what%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20food%E2%80%9D%20is.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20village%2C%20we%20have%20eaten%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edheki%20ka%20chaawal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20we%20know%20how%20to%20pound%20and%20mill%20paddy%20into%20rice%20ourselves%20at%20home%2C%20in%20small%20batches.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emaarh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%5Bstarch%5D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20that%20rice%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eis%20so%20thick%2C%20it%20contains%20nutrients%20from%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLocally%2C%20we%20have%20paddy%20varieties%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMakarkanthi%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaankri%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENohaachi-dhaan%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENohaachi-dhaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20thick%20bran%20is%20red%2C%20almost%20black%2C%20in%20colour%20with%20grains%20filled%20with%20nutrients.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emaarh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20delicious%20%E2%80%93%20thicker%20than%20milk%20with%20Horlicks!%20Yet%2C%20the%20local%20rice%20is%20light%20and%20easy%20to%20digest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGope%20who%20is%20the%20traditional%20headman%20of%20his%20village%20Panajea%2C%20was%20not%20only%20unconvinced%20by%20the%20government%20policy%20on%20rice%20fortification%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20also%20alarmed%20and%20anxious.%20He%20believed%20that%20the%20new%20fortified%20grains%20may%20not%20be%20suitable%20for%20those%20who%20are%20not%20well.%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%2C%20not%20everyone%20will%20be%20able%20to%20digest%20this%20new%20rice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20since%20this%20rice%20started%20being%20distributed%2C%20we%20have%20had%20two%20instances%20where%20people%20who%20fell%20ill%20needed%20blood%20transfusions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20rice%20has%20additional%20vitamins%2C%20then%20why%20is%20that%20happening%3F%20How%20do%20we%20know%20if%20it%20is%20even%20helping%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAt%20risk%20and%20uncertain%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInside%20Panajea%20village%2C%20this%20reporter%20met%20one%20of%20the%20individuals%20whose%20health%20Gope%20was%20concerned%20about.%20Rahul%20Gope%2C%20a%20quiet%20teenager%20dressed%20in%20a%20t-shirt%20and%20shorts%2C%20had%20a%20slight%20build%2C%20which%20made%20him%20appear%20smaller%20than%20his%20age.%20His%20face%20was%20pale%20and%20his%20eyes%20had%20turned%20yellow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Chherani%20Gope%20shared%20multiple%20laboratory%20reports%20that%20showed%20how%20Rahul%20had%20undergone%20two%20blood%20transfusions%20in%20the%20previous%20three%20weeks%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20his%20life%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20first%20blood%20transfusion%2C%20laboratory%20reports%20showed%2C%20he%20had%20a%20blood%20haemoglobin%20level%20%E2%80%93%20an%20essential%20protein%20carrying%20oxygen%20in%20the%20body%20%E2%80%93%20of%20merely%205.9.%20This%20was%20not%20even%20half%20of%20the%20healthy%20norm%20for%20his%20age.%20He%20was%20severely%20anaemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reports%20also%20showed%20excess%20bilirubin%2C%20more%20than%20three%20times%20the%20normal%2C%20showing%20an%20excess%20in%20his%20body%20of%20a%20pigment%20formed%20from%20a%20breakdown%20of%20blood%20cells.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065645%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065645%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065645%2FUntitled-design-12-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065645%2FUntitled-design-12-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%E2%80%99s%20mother%20Chherani%20Gope%20shared%20medical%20reports%20that%20showed%20no%20clear%20diagnosis%20of%20his%20severe%20anaemia%2C%20accompanied%20with%20jaundice.%20Photos%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20family%20said%20they%20had%20spent%20more%20than%20Rs%2020%2C000%20on%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20nearest%20health%20facility%20and%20laboratory%2C%2040%20km%20away%20in%20Jhargram%20in%20Bengal%20(the%20neighbouring%20state)%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20have%20a%20diagnosis%20for%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20condition.%20They%20live%20more%20than%20100%20km%20away%20from%20Jamshedpur%20city%2C%20where%20tertiary%20health%20facilities%20are%20located.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20mandatory%20rice%20fortification%20in%20public%20schemes%20is%20a%20response%20to%20chronically%20high%20levels%20of%20anaemia%20in%20the%20Indian%20population%2C%20which%20manifests%2C%20among%20other%20forms%2C%20in%20low%20haemoglobin%20levels%20such%20as%20Rahul%E2%80%99s.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20government%20acknowledges%20that%20it%20could%20potentially%20harm%20those%20like%20him%2C%20whose%20low%20haemoglobin%20could%20be%20a%20result%20of%20other%20conditions%20such%20as%20inherited%20blood%20disorders%20prevalent%20in%20this%20region%E2%80%99s%20Adivasi%20residents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20these%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-and-diseases%2Fsickle-cell-disease%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esickle%20cell%20disease%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20blood%20disorder%20caused%20by%20a%20genetic%20mutation.%20In%20it%2C%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20blood%20cells%20are%20misshapen%2C%20like%20sickles%20or%20crescents.%20Such%20misshapen%20cells%20can%20get%20stuck%20in%20blood%20vessels%2C%20causing%20organ%20damage%2C%20debilitating%20pain%2C%20and%20strokes.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20largely%20affects%20Adivasi%20communities.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-and-diseases%2Fthalassemias%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThalassemia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20another%20inherited%20blood%20disorder%20caused%20by%20damaged%20or%20missing%20genes%20in%20which%20the%20body%20does%20not%20make%20adequate%20haemoglobin.%20It%20is%20managed%20with%20regular%20blood%20transfusions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065840%2F3.3_Sickle_Cells-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22903%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065840%2F3.3_Sickle_Cells-1.jpeg%20903w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21065840%2F3.3_Sickle_Cells-1-300x266.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685620%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIn%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%2C%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20misshapen%20blood%20cells%20look%20like%20sickles%2C%20and%20can%20block%20the%20major%20blood%20vessels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20each%20gunny%20bag%20containing%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20carries%20a%20warning%20in%20small%20print%20in%20English%20%E2%80%93%20a%20language%20neither%20understood%20nor%20spoken%20by%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20poor%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20fortified%20rice%20is%20not%20meant%20for%20those%20with%20conditions%20such%20as%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20and%20thalassemia.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20effect%20of%20additional%20iron%20stores%20from%20iron%20fortified%20food%20is%20not%20clear%20or%20known%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0002916523233171%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuch%20individuals%E2%80%99%20bodies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20If%20the%20excess%20iron%20gets%20stored%2C%20it%20may%20potentially%20damage%20their%20organs%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Frice-fortification-programme-iron-anaemia-7470938%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esay%20experts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20symptoms%20Rahul%20was%20suffering%20from%20%E2%80%93%20very%20low%20haemoglobin%20combined%20with%20jaundice%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20seen%20in%20those%20with%20sickle%20cell%20disease.%20But%20that%20afternoon%2C%20Rahul%20had%20neither%20any%20information%20nor%20access%20to%20tests%20to%20determine%20whether%20he%20was%20among%20those%20who%20ought%20to%20avoid%20eating%20the%20iron%20fortified%20rice.%20Nor%20was%20any%20alternate%20food%20provided%20to%20him%20in%20the%20public%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Diktat%E2%80%99%20to%20feed%20fortified%20rice%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficials%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Ranchi%2C%20180%20km%20away%2C%20who%20run%20the%20scheme%20to%20distribute%20ration%20rice%2C%20said%20they%20lack%20information%20on%20how%20many%20of%20existing%20food%20rations%20card%20holders%20in%20Jharkhand%20already%20suffer%20from%20such%20%E2%80%9Chemoglobinopathies%E2%80%9D%2C%20disorders%20such%20as%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20or%20thalassemia%2C%20and%20are%20thus%20supposed%20to%20avoid%20eating%20the%20iron-fortified%20rice.%20Nor%20did%20the%20department%20have%20provisions%20to%20give%20them%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20chemically%20fortified%20rice%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20continuing%20to%20provide%20them%20custom%20milled%20rice%20as%20it%20did%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20positive%20thing%20is%20that%20since%20the%20distribution%20of%20iron-fortified%20rice%20began%2C%20we%20have%20not%20got%20an%20adverse%20health%20report%20from%20the%20field%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20government%2C%20overseeing%20the%20new%20policy%E2%80%99s%20implementation%2C%20stated%20about%20his%20discomfort%20with%20the%20scheme.%20He%20added%20that%20when%20several%20critics%2C%20including%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20former%20minister%20for%20food%20and%20civil%20supplies%20Sarayu%20Roy%2C%20publicly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flagatar24.com%2Fformer-food-and-civil-supply-minister-saryu-roy-raises-doubt-on-quality-of-fortified-rice-distributed-under-pds%2F91094%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopposed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20scheme%2C%20to%20improve%20public%20understanding%2C%20the%20department%20had%20organised%20workshops%2C%20inviting%20medical%20experts%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%2C%20organisations%20who%20work%20on%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%20and%20civil%20society%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A7%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%A1%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82.%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B9%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B5%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A5%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88.%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B9%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%83%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88.%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B8%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%9F%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%81%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%2C%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%8F.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Saryu%20Roy%20(%40roysaryu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Froysaryu%2Fstatus%2F1512745141823754242%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%209%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EThe%20official%20said%20that%20the%20Jharkhand%20state%20government%2C%20which%20looks%20after%20the%20health%20and%20nutrition%20needs%20of%20some%20of%20the%20poorest%20communities%20of%20India%2C%20was%20provided%20no%20choice%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20implementing%20this%20new%20policy%2C%20even%20when%20Jharkhand%20lacks%20adequate%20infrastructure%2C%20such%20as%20laboratories%20which%20can%20test%20the%20added%20micronutrient%20content%2C%20to%20ensure%20quality%20control%20and%20safety.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20came%20to%20this%3A%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%2C%20which%20supplies%20us%20the%20rice%20which%20we%20distribute%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20said%20that%20if%20you%20do%20not%20take%20chemically%20fortified%20rice%2C%20you%20will%20not%20get%20any%20rice.%20Then%20the%20public%20grain%20distribution%20in%20Jharkhand%20would%20stop%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20official.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Jharkhand%2C%20so%20far%2C%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%2C%20under%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%2C%20acted%20as%20an%20aggregator.%20Under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%2C%20it%20procured%20paddy%20and%20provided%20it%20to%20Jharkhand%20from%20a%20central%20pool.%20After%20the%20paddy%20is%20milled%2C%20it%20is%20transported%20to%20FCI%20warehouses%2C%20and%20then%20the%20state-level%20bodies%20distribute%20it%20further%20at%20retail%20outlets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20food%20ministry%20told%20us%3A%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20wish%20to%20distribute%20simple%20%E2%80%9Ccustom%20made%20rice%E2%80%9D%20(CMR)%20like%20before%2C%20then%20make%20your%20own%20arrangements%20for%20that.%E2%80%99%20The%20Jharkhand%20state%20government%20does%20not%20have%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20do%20so%2C%20without%20FCI%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20stated.%20%E2%80%9CState%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eko%20unhone%20majboor%20kiya%20ki%20aap%20ko%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Efortified%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20lena%20hi%20hai%2C%20doosra%20koi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eoption%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20nahi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20(They%20made%20it%20compulsory%20for%20us%2C%20giving%20us%20no%20option%20but%20to%20distribute%20fortified%20food.)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Mandatory%E2%80%99%20scheme%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20selected%20a%20district%20each%20in%2015%20states%20to%20distribute%20fortified%20rice%20as%20a%20pilot%20scheme.%20It%20started%20distributing%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20food%20safety%20programmes%20in%202022.%20It%20plans%20to%20expand%20this%20scheme%20to%20all%20districts%20of%20India%20by%20March%202024%20with%20a%20yearly%20budget%20of%20nearly%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%2C%20or%20%24350%20million%20approximately.%20From%20March%202022%2C%20it%20made%20fortified%20rice%20compulsory%20in%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20schemes.%20From%20March%202023%20onwards%2C%20it%20introduced%20it%20in%20ration%2C%20or%20the%20public%20distribution%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20ration%20scheme%20is%20the%20largest%20food%20safety%20scheme%20in%20the%20world%2C%20reaching%2080%20crore%20or%20800%20million%20individuals.%20For%20a%20comparison%2C%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme(WFP)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wfp.org%2Fstories%2Fwfp-glance%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEach%2520month%2520WFP%2520supports%2520around%2Cwith%2520food%252C%2520cash%2520or%2520vouchers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereached%20160%20million%20people%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202022.%20After%20years%20of%20advocacy%20by%20grassroots%20activists%E2%80%99%20networks%20such%20as%20the%20Right%20to%20Food%20Campaign%2C%20the%20previous%20government%20expanded%20food%20security%20schemes%20to%20include%2067%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population.%20Under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%2C%202013%2C%20every%20member%20of%20a%20poor%20household%20receives%20five%20kg%20of%20grains%2C%20wheat%20or%20rice%2C%20at%20very%20low%20costs%20at%20village%20ration%20shops.%20The%20poorest%20households%20get%2035%20kg%20grains%20each%20month.%20Under%20the%20midday%20meal%20programme%2C%20115%20million%20school%20children%20get%20a%20hot%20cooked%20meal%20daily%2C%20and%20under%20the%20Integrated%20Child%20Development%20Scheme(ICDS)%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20early%20childcare%20program%2C%20158%20million%20infants%2C%20pregnant%20and%20lactating%20women%2C%20get%20supplementary%20nutrition%20at%20community%20creches.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20ICDS%20and%20school%20lunch%20schemes%2C%20the%20government%20supplies%20around%203.5%20million(35%20lakh)%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20iron-fortified%20rice.%20This%20increases%20ten-fold%20to%20more%20than%2035%20million%20(350%20lakh)%20metric%20tonnes%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20public%20distribution%20scheme%2C%20when%20scaled%20to%20all%20districts%20by%202024.%20In%20October%20this%20year%2C%20the%20government%20distributed%20nearly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fannavitran.nic.in%2FFR%2FavFortifiedRice%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E17%2C74%2C153%20metric%20tonnes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20fortified%20rice%20in%20its%20welfare%20schemes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgh.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F6%2F2%2Fe004322%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esecond%20highest%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20burden%20incidence%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20children%20with%20thalassemia-major%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20government%20has%20provided%20a%20few%20numbers%20in%20parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%209%2C%202021%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fgovernance%2Fas-told-to-parliament-august-9-2021-no-data-on-sickle-cell-disease-among-tribals-78365%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresponding%20to%20a%20parliament%20question%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20tribal%20affairs%20Renuka%20Singh%20Saruta%20replied%20that%201%2C13%2C83%2C664%20(1.13%20crore%20or%2011.3%20million)%20persons%20in%20India%20were%20screened%20for%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20and%20%E2%80%9C8.75%25%20(9%2C96%2C368%2C%20or%209%20million)%20tested%20positive%20(trait%20in%20949057%2C%20disease%2047%2C311).%E2%80%9D%20Further%2C%20the%20minister%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cstudies%20undertaken%20by%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20show%20prevalence%20of%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%20across%20the%20country%20is%205-34%25%20(as%20per%20document%20on%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%20control%20programme%20published%20by%20Government%20of%20Gujarat)%E2%80%9D.%20On%20a%20question%20about%20thalassemia%2C%20on%20March%2020%2C%202020%2C%20the%20government%20replied%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Can%20estimated%2010%2C000-12%2C000%20children%20with%20B%20(the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-and-diseases%2Fbeta-thalassemia%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebeta)-Thalassemia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20born%20every%20year%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20pilots%20conducted%20for%20launching%20the%20intervention%2C%20the%20government%20tested%20how%20the%20supply%20chain%20of%20fortified%20rice%20works%20%E2%80%93%20or%20how%20it%20would%20reach%20from%20the%20manufacturing%20unit%20to%20a%20rice%20mill%2C%20to%20government%20godowns%20to%20retail%20rations%20shops.%20It%20did%20not%20study%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20intervention%20on%20public%20health%2C%20or%20on%20anaemia%2C%20or%20how%20the%20individuals%20with%20certain%20health%20conditions%20would%20tolerate%20this%20rice.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActivists%20pointed%20out%20that%20despite%20significant%20populations%20being%20at%20risk%2C%20the%20government%20launched%20the%20scheme%20without%20safeguarding%20how%20individuals%20with%20such%20blood%20disorders%20would%20be%20affected%20when%20they%20ate%20the%20fortified%20food%2C%20or%20how%20their%20bodies%20would%20react%20to%20the%20additional%20synthetic%20iron%20in%20food.%20Not%20only%20activists%2C%20but%20even%20members%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20panels%20have%20publicly%20spoken%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS000291652200452X%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eagainst%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20giving%20such%20rice%20to%20those%20suffering%20from%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20and%20thalassemia%20patients.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20iron-fortified%20food%20should%20also%20not%20be%20given%20to%20those%20with%20other%20conditions%20such%20as%20severe%20malnutrition%2C%20and%20newly%20diagnosed%20tuberculosis%2C%20said%20Dr%20Sylvia%20Karpagam%2C%20a%20doctor%20and%20public%20health%20researcher%2C%20who%20works%20on%20right%20to%20health%20and%20nutrition%20among%20marginalised%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CMalnutrition%20and%20tuberculosis%20can%20often%20remain%20undiagnosed%20and%20untreated%20in%20India.%20Then%2C%20why%20are%20policymakers%20surging%20ahead%20with%20iron%20fortification%20of%20rice%20on%20such%20a%20large%20and%20irreversible%20scale%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Dr%20Karpagam.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20because%20these%20conditions%20affect%20the%20poor%20more%20than%20the%20elite%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21070338%2F5.-health-advisory-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21070338%2F5.-health-advisory-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21070338%2F5.-health-advisory-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21070338%2F5.-health-advisory-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EEach%20gunny%20bag%20of%20fortified%20rice%20in%20the%20ration%20system%20carries%20a%20health%20warning%20in%20small%20print%20in%20English%2C%20a%20language%20neither%20understood%20nor%20spoken%20by%20the%20majority%20of%20poor.%20Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBalram%2C%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Food%20Campaign%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20study%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20fortified%20rice%20scheme%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tracked%20it%20in%20four%20villages%20in%20two%20pilot%20blocks.%20Printing%20a%20health%20warning%20in%20small%20print%20in%20English%20in%20rural%20areas%20is%20totally%20ineffective.%20And%20anyway%2C%20the%20rice%20is%20distributed%20to%20the%20poor%20as%20loose%20grains%2C%20not%20in%20bags%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20formal%20warning%2C%20we%20found%20grassroots%20health%20workers%20had%20no%20instructions%20to%20make%20this%20distinction%20for%20the%20affected%20individuals%20in%20the%20villages.%20It%20shows%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20utter%20lack%20of%20concern.%20There%20are%20no%20real%20safeguards%20to%20enforce%20it.%20Yet%2C%20the%20scheme%20has%20been%20scaled%20up%2C%20like%20a%20royal%20diktat%20disregarding%20the%20palate%2C%20food%20habits%2C%20taste%20of%20millions.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActivist%20Rajesh%20Krishnan%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20campaign%2C%20filed%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20December%20over%20the%20impact%20on%20health%20of%20such%20vulnerable%20groups.%20Hearing%20the%20case%20last%20month%2C%20the%20court%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20respond%20in%20November.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20evidence%20the%20Union%20government%20considered%20in%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20favour%20was%20a%20randomised%20control%20trial%20(a%20study%20in%20which%20two%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20one%20which%20receives%20an%20intervention%20and%20the%20other%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%93%20are%20compared)%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20fortified%20rice%20on%20reducing%20anaemia%20conducted%20by%20the%20Tata%20Trusts%2C%20which%20is%20a%20philanthropic%20initiative%20of%20the%20Indian%20multinational%20Tata%20Sons.%20The%20Bill%20and%20Melinda%20Gates%20Foundation%20(BMGF)%20has%20funded%20Tata%20Trusts%20to%20advocate%20for%20and%20work%20on%20fortification%20in%20India.%20For%20instance%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gatesfoundation.org%2Fabout%2Fcommitted-grants%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20gave%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3ESir%20Dorabji%20Tata%20Trusts%20US%20%24%203%20million%20for%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CFood%20Fortification%20MIYCN%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ematernal%20and%20child%20nutrition)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Joint%20Programming%20Platform%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%202016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFood%20and%20health%20activists%20have%20criticised%20relying%20on%20such%20sources%20which%20were%20conducting%20%E2%80%9Cfriendly%20research%E2%80%9D%20financed%20by%20lobbying%20groups%20as%20a%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20Tata%20is%20a%20conglomerate%20which%20owns%20several%20businesses%2C%20including%20in%20chemicals%2C%20food%20and%20in%20nutraceutical%20sectors.%20Moreover%2C%20even%20this%20promotional%20study%20conducted%20by%20Tata%20Trusts%20in%20Gadchiroli%20district%2C%20one%20of%20the%20poorest%20parts%20of%20Maharashtra%20in%20western%20India%2C%20which%20is%20a%20glowing%20evaluation%20of%20such%20an%20intervention%2C%20was%20cautious%20on%20providing%20the%20rice%20to%20those%20with%20sickle%20cell%20disease.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortification.fssai.gov.in%2Fassets%2Fevent%2Ffile%2Fimpact-assesment-of-rice-fortification-dr-dk.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETata%20Trusts%20study%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20recorded%20a%20%E2%80%9Closs%20of%20sample%E2%80%9D.%20It%20had%20to%20exclude%20a%20sizeable%20number%20of%20individuals%20from%20the%20study%20sample%20because%20it%20found%20they%20%E2%80%9Csuffered%20from%20sickle%20cell%20disease%E2%80%9D.%20Ministries%E2%80%99%20correspondence%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reporters-collective.in%2Fprojects%2Fmodified-rice-papers%5C%22%3Efirst%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Reporters%E2%80%99%20Collective%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20in%20blood%20tests%2C%20%E2%80%9C7.4%25%20mothers%20at%20Kurkheda%2C%2017.1%25%20at%20Bhamragarh%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9C15%25%20adolescent%20girls%20at%20Kurkheda%2C%2010.3%25%20at%20Bhamragarh%E2%80%9D%20and%20among%20children%2C%20%E2%80%9C9.5%25%20at%20Kurkheda%2C%208.2%25%20at%20Bhamragarh%E2%80%9D%20were%20found%20to%20%E2%80%9Chave%20sickle%20cell%20disease%E2%80%9D.%20The%20evaluators%20avoided%20feeding%20iron-fortified%20rice%20to%20these%20women%2C%20adolescents%20and%20children%20who%20suffered%20from%20the%20blood%20disorder%20resulting%20from%20a%20flawed%20haemoglobin%20mechanism%20in%20their%20bodies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21070810%2F5.2-Tata-Trusts-Study-recorded-loss-of-sample-from-sickle-cell-anemia.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21070810%2F5.2-Tata-Trusts-Study-recorded-loss-of-sample-from-sickle-cell-anemia.png%20884w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21070810%2F5.2-Tata-Trusts-Study-recorded-loss-of-sample-from-sickle-cell-anemia-300x66.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685622%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22195%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Tata%20Trusts%20study%20recorded%20that%20they%20could%20not%20study%20those%20with%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20had%20ignored%20that%20even%20such%20studies%2C%20financed%20by%20entities%20such%20as%20Tata%2C%20had%20avoided%20giving%20this%20rice%20to%20vulnerable%20groups.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20all%20studies%2C%20certain%20groups%20are%20excluded%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20fully%20know%20or%20understand%20the%20impact%20on%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20explained%20a%20doctor%20working%20in%20the%20government%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20be%20named.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20way%20to%20know%20the%20full%20impact%20on%20such%20groups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMedical%20experts%20explained%20one%20of%20the%20less%20understood%20concerns%2C%20firstly%2C%20how%20excess%20iron%20may%20get%20stored%20in%20a%20form%20that%20was%20of%20no%20use%20to%20the%20body%2C%20and%20secondly%2C%20it%20could%20do%20harm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CStudies%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0002916523233171%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshow%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20some%20such%20patients%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20down-regulate%20their%20iron%20absorption%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20absorb%20iron.%20The%20problem%20with%20excess%20iron%20is%20that%20it%20ends%20up%20in%20a%20toxic%20form%20in%20the%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20explained%20Dr%20Anura%20Kurpad%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20St%20John%E2%80%99s%20Medical%20College%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20who%20chaired%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%E2%80%99s%20(ICMR)%20expert%20committee%20on%20nutrient%20requirements%2C%20and%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20scientific%20committee%20of%20the%20food%20regulatory%20body%2C%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThis%20excess%20iron%20that%20is%20unbound%20to%20the%20usual%20transport%20protein%20called%20transferrin%20is%20(quite%20unimaginatively)%20called%20%E2%80%9Cnon%20transferrin%20bound%20iron%E2%80%9D%20or%20NTBI.%20This%20is%20particularly%20toxic%20as%20it%20forms%20reactive%20oxidative%20species%20that%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20damage%20to%20cells.%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Kurpad%20said%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccardiac%20damage%2C%20liver%20fibrosis%2C%20gonadal%20dysfunction%2C%20and%20growth%20retardation%2C%20among%20many%20others%E2%80%9D%20for%20such%20individuals.%20Dr%20Kurpad%20further%20said%20that%20the%20storage%20form%20of%20iron%20%E2%80%93%20ferritin%20%E2%80%93%20would%20also%20increase%2C%20with%20increased%20rick%20of%20chronic%20diseases%20like%20diabetes.%20In%20the%20European%20Journal%20of%20Clinical%20Nutrition%2C%20Dr%20Kurpad%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41430-022-01222-2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshowed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20this%20was%20linked%20to%20increased%20risks%20among%20adolescents%20of%20non-communicable%20disease.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20must%20be%20a%20mechanism%20for%20the%20problem%20of%20balancing%20the%20risks%20and%20benefits%20of%20iron%20supplementation%20in%20these%20areas%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20no%20shortcut%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriticism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20activists%20and%20academics%2C%20the%20food%20safety%20regulator%2C%20FSSAI%20in%20August%202021%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fssai.gov.in%2Fupload%2Fuploadfiles%2Ffiles%2FCompendium_Food_Fortification_Regulations_30_09_2021.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eissued%20a%20gazette%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20adding%20%E2%80%9Cpersons%20with%20Sickle%20Cell%20Anemia%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20language%20of%20its%20fortification%20regulations%20of%202018%2C%20advising%20them%20not%20to%20consume%20%E2%80%9Ciron%20fortified%20products%E2%80%9D.%20Taking%20no%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20this%2C%20it%20left%20it%20to%20already%20overburdened%20health%20departments%20in%20states%20to%20identify%20and%20protect%20such%20persons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20mid-2021%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1744094%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eset%20up%20a%20Sickle%20Cell%20Disease%20Support%20Corner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Piramal%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Piramal%20Swasthya%20Management%20and%20Research%20Institute%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20a%20database%20of%20individuals%20with%20sickle%20cell%20disease%2C%20or%20traits%20in%20the%20tribal%20population%E2%80%9D.%20Under%20this%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1953322%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20is%20carrying%20out%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20%E2%80%9Cuniversal%20screening%20of%207%20crore%20people%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%200-40%20years%20in%20affected%20tribal%20areas%E2%80%9D.%20Piramal%20Foundation%20is%20the%20philanthropy%20arm%20of%20US%20%24%204%20billion-worth%20Piramal%20Group%20of%20Companies.%20The%20Swiss%20pharmaceutical%2C%20Hoffman-La%20Roche%20Ltd.%2C%20which%20was%20then%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20multinational%20company%20making%20synthetic%20vitamins%20had%20sold%20its%20India%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.joc.com%2Farticle%2Fhoffmann-la-roche-sells-stake-india-venture-piramal_19931104.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebusiness%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20majority%20stakes%20to%20Piramal.%20Piramal%20Group%20includes%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.piramalpharmasolutions.com%2Fnutrition-solutions%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enutraceutical%20business%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20manufacturing%20synthetic%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortification.fssai.gov.in%2Fassets%2Ffile%2FCentral_License_Premix.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20among%20the%20suppliers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20factory-made%20nutrients%20in%20the%20government%20fortification%20programme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPublic%20health%20experts%20expressed%20wariness%20at%20the%20involvement%20of%20nutraceutical-funded%20entities%20which%20advocated%20for%20the%20mandatory%20fortification%20of%20staples%2C%20and%20they%20questioned%20the%20ethics%20of%20such%20a%20mass%20screening%20of%20millions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20mass%2C%20universal%20screening%20for%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%20raises%20ethical%20concerns%20because%20youth%20diagnosed%20with%20it%20may%20face%20discrimination%20in%20jobs%2C%20marriage%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Yogesh%20Jain%2C%20a%20community%20physician%20who%20has%20treated%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20patients%20in%20rural%20Adivasi%20areas%20in%20north%20Chhattisgarh.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20may%20be%20good%20to%20ensure%20complete%20diagnosis%20to%20those%20who%20are%20symptomatic%2C%20and%20once%20achieved%2C%20screen%20pregnant%20women%2C%20or%20newborns.%20Once%20that%20is%20done%2C%20you%20may%20consider%20mass%20screening%20after%20consulting%20with%20all%20communities%20and%20be%20ethically%20correct.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Jain%20added%20that%20he%20did%20not%20view%20mandatory%20iron%20fortification%20of%20rice%20as%20a%20cure%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20anaemic%20population%2C%20because%20nutritional%20deficiency%20is%20the%20cause%20of%2060%25%20of%20all%20anaemia%20and%20iron%20deficiency%20is%20the%20cause%20of%20two-thirds%20of%20nutrition%20deficiency.%20Thus%2C%20iron%20deficiency%20anaemia%20constitutes%20the%20cause%20in%20less%20than%20half%20of%20all%20anaemia%20cases%2C%20the%20other%20causes%20being%20inflammation%2C%20or%20infections.%20%E2%80%9CLarge%20scale%20food%20fortification%20is%20a%20rent-seeking%20approach%20shrouded%20as%20a%20technological%20fix%2C%20where%20companies%20profit%20from%20making%20and%20blending%20nutrients.%20How%20will%20it%20help%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Jain.%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20fortified%20rice%20in%20this%20form%20does%20not%20even%20adequately%20help%20the%20iron-deficient.%20It%20is%20corroborated%20by%20studies%20that%20food-based%20corrections%2C%20such%20as%20providing%20iron%20in%20the%20diet%20along%20with%20a%20fruit%2C%20would%20be%20better.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21071251%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-7.12.12.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21071251%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-7.12.12.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21071251%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-7.12.12-300x210.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21071251%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-at-7.12.12-1024x715.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685623%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPublic%20health%20experts%20say%20access%20to%20eating%20fresh%2C%20diverse%20foods%20such%20as%20citrus%20fruits%20will%20help%20an%20individual%20in%20better%20absorbing%20iron%20from%20food%20sources.%20Photo%3A%20Anumeha%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20appointed%20PATH%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%20partner%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jharkhand%20to%20help%20implement%20the%20scheme.%C2%A0%20PATH%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cproduct%20development%20organisation%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20initiated%20by%20Ford%20Foundation%20in%201977%2C%20which%20is%20heavily%20funded%20by%20the%20Bill%20and%20Melinda%20Gates%20Foundation%2C%20with%20which%20it%20has%20long%20standing%20institutional%20ties.%20In%201998%2C%20before%20the%20official%20establishment%20of%20the%20Gates%20Foundation%2C%20Gates%20created%20the%20Bill%20%26amp%3B%20Melinda%20Gates%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Vaccine%20Programme%20with%20a%20donation%20of%20%24100%20million%20and%20this%20was%20administered%20by%20PATH%E2%80%99s%20secretariat%20in%20Seattle.%20As%20per%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20financial%20report%2C%2043%25%20of%20its%20funding%20was%20from%20one%20private%20foundation%2C%20and%2032%25%20from%20United%20States%20government%20agencies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20this%20was%2048%25%20and%2023%25%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fcontent%2Farticle%2Findian-parliament-comes-down-hard-cervical-cancer-trial%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehalted%20a%20trial%20by%20PATH%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(funded%20by%20the%20Gates%20Foundation)%20among%20Adivasi%20children%2C%20in%20which%20it%20was%20testing%20vaccines%20against%20cervical%20cancer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhsrii.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F07%2F72.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2013%20report%20by%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20health%20found%20collusion%20between%20Indian%20health%20regulators%20and%20PATH%20to%20downplay%20the%20violations%20in%20this%20vaccine%20trial.%20It%20found%20that%20PATH%20had%20described%20the%20project%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cobservational%20study%E2%80%9D%20and%20circumvented%20rules%20around%20such%20trials%2C%20such%20as%20reporting%20of%20serious%20adverse%20effects%20within%20a%20specific%20time.%20The%20parliamentary%20enquiry%20found%20that%20PATH%20had%20violated%20children%E2%80%99s%20rights.%20It%20had%20collected%20data%20on%20a%20large%20population%20of%2023%2C500%20children%20of%20age%2010%20to%2014.%20In%20the%20case%20of%205%2C000%20children%2C%20the%20parents%2Fguardians%20were%20not%20literate%20and%20could%20not%20even%20sign%20in%20their%20local%20language%2C%20in%20Telugu%20or%20Gujarati%2C%20and%20in%20Andhra%2C%20had%20simply%20obtained%20the%20consent%20from%20hostel%20wardens%20of%20residential%20schools%20the%20Adivasi%20children%20were%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.piramalswasthya.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSwasthya-FCRA-returns-Q2-FY-23-24.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elatest%20financial%20documents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Piramal%20Swasthya%20Management%20and%20Research%20Institute%2C%20which%20is%20running%20a%20%E2%80%9Csupport%20corner%E2%80%9D%20for%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20and%20is%20tasked%20with%20creating%20a%20database%20of%20individuals%20with%20sickle%20disease%20or%20traits%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20population%2C%20in%20the%20financial%20quarter%20July%20to%20September%202023%2C%20the%20Gates%20Foundation%20donated%20to%20it%20Rs%2018%20crore%20as%20a%20grant%2C%20and%20PATH%20gave%20it%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%201.4%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActivists%20critiqued%20the%20conflict%20of%20interest%20inherent%20in%20these%20policies.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20for-profit%20entity%20of%20the%20business%20is%20first%20supplying%20the%20fortificant%20earning%20profits%2C%20and%20the%20not-for-profit%20part%20of%20the%20same%20entity%20is%20managing%20the%20potential%20health%20harms%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Soumik%20Banerjee%2C%20one%20of%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20RTF%20and%20the%20Alliance%20for%20Sustainable%20and%20Holistic%20Agriculture%20(ASHA)%20fact-finding%20report%20on%20the%20scheme%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20Referring%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20delayed%20advisory%20for%20those%20with%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%20to%20avoid%20eating%20fortified%20rice%2C%20he%20called%20mandatory%20fortification%20%E2%80%9Ca%20wasteful%20strategy%20for%20the%20most%2C%20while%20