identified%20in%20the%20report%20said%20the%20criticism%20was%20exaggerated.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20critics%20are%20wrong.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20there%20is%20evidence%20that%20fortified%20rice%20will%20address%20anaemia%2C%20on%20the%20other%2C%20in%20India%2C%20it%20is%20being%20done%20such%20that%20it%20would%20meet%20only%2025%25%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20recommended%20dietary%20allowance%2C%20thus%2C%20there%20is%20very%20little%20scope%20of%20toxicity%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20these%20critics%20say%20that%20individuals%20are%20at%20risk%2C%20if%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20those%20with%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%20is%20not%20even%20known%2C%20then%20where%20are%20they%20getting%20data%20to%20ask%20such%20questions%20from%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20clear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Gates%20Foundation%20and%20PATH%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20an%20emailed%20questionnaire%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20advocacy%20for%20mandatory%20fortification%2C%20the%20experimentation%20and%20its%20potential%20side%20effects%20on%20vulnerable%20populations%2C%20including%20those%20with%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98How%20can%20we%20eat%20it%20when%20the%20birds%20don%E2%80%99t%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJawahar%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20in%20Palamu%2C%20questioned%20why%20fortified%20rice%20had%20been%20mandatory.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20is%20harmful%20for%20some%20group%20of%20people%2C%20such%20as%20those%20with%20thalassemia%20or%20sickle%20cell%20disease%2C%20why%20is%20it%20being%20given%20to%20anyone%20at%20all%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20He%20said%20there%20was%20little%20social%20acceptance%20of%20the%20new%20grains%20even%20months%20after%20they%20had%20been%20introduced%2C%20and%20several%20questions%20remained.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20wonder%20why%20isn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%9Cplastic%