5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20assume%20here%20that%20%E2%80%9CMe%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20last%20verse%20refers%20not%20to%20God%2C%20or%20the%20Supreme%20Being%2C%20but%20to%20Cricket%2C%20our%20most%20beloved%20game%20(and%20secular%20national%20religion).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20as%20a%20man%20in%20his%20seventh%20decade%20of%20life%20%E2%80%93%20who%20watched%20his%20first%20Test%20match%2C%20at%20age%207%2C%20in%201969%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20remarkable%20thing%20about%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20final%20was%20that%20so%20many%20neutrals%20everywhere%20(by%20which%20I%20mean%20cricket%20fans%20who%20weren%E2%80%99t%20Indian%20or%20Australian)%20were%20cheering%20not%20for%20India%20but%20for%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20the%20End%2C%20It%E2%80%99s%20Always%20XI%20Versus%20XI%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-australia-cricket-world-cup-final-gideon-haigh%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20End%2C%20It%E2%80%99s%20Always%20XI%20Versus%20XI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20because%20India%20weren%E2%80%99t%20the%20underdogs%20in%20the%20final%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20why%20neutrals%20don%E2%80%99t%20back%20a%20particular%20competitor.%20But%20being%20better%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20put%20neutrals%20off.%20Few%20non-Englishmen%20cheered%20for%20England%20in%20the%201979%20final%2C%20preferring%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20then%20favoured%20so%20heavily%20to%20win%20that%20their%20losing%20would%20have%20been%20a%20cosmic%20shock%20(as%20it%20was%20in%201983%2C%20when%20they%20lost%20to%20India%2C%20back%20then%20a%20kinder%20country%20than%20it%20is%20now%2C%20more%20self-effacing%2C%20less%20triumphalist%20and%20ugly).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeutrals%20cheered%20Australia%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20team%20that%20has%20historically%20been%20unloved%20outside%20its%20own%20shores%2C%20because%20most%20cricket%20fans%20worldwide%20are%20thoroughly%20sick%20%E2%80%93%20fed%20up%2C%20pissed%20off%20%E2%80%93%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20bully-boy%20dominance%20of%20world%20cricket.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20sporting%20dominance%2C%20which%20neutral%20fans%20can%20live%20with%20(as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20the%20West%20Indians%20of%20the%20Clive%20Lloyd%20and%20Viv%20Richards%20era%2C%20or%20Brazilian%20football%20in%20the%20time%20of%20Pel%C3%A9).%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20wholesale%20takeover%20by%20the%20BCCI%20of%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20financing%2C%20values%2C%20and%20calendar%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20grip%20over%20the%20game%20that%20is%20stronger%2C%20more%20ruthless%20and%20vice-like%2C%20more%20absolute%20and%20remorseless%2C%20more%20self-serving%20and%20mercantilist%2C%20than%20that%20once%20exercised%20by%20the%20game%E2%80%99s%20original%20overlords%20in%20England%20(who%20might%2C%20at%20some%20level%2C%20have%20been%20forgiven%20their%20assertion%20of%20ownership%20over%20cricket%20because%20they%20did%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20give%20us%20the%20game).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20has%20warped%20cricket%2C%20distorted%20it%2C%20making%20it%20so%20India-centric%20that%20other%20proud%20nations%20%E2%80%93%20some%20with%20better%20pedigrees%20than%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20bit-part%20players%2C%20mendicants%2C%20petitioners%20for%20match-time.%20Everything%20is%20now%20about%20India%3A%20the%20crowds%2C%20the%20songs%2C%20the%20scheduling%2C%20the%20pitches%2C%20the%20money.%20The%20one%20element%20the%20BCCI%20cannot%20control%2C%20mercifully%2C%20is%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20match.%20Try%20as%20the%20BJP%20might%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20BCCI%20is%20now%20the%20BJP%20in%20cricketing%20form%20%E2%80%93%20the%20result%20of%20a%20match%20cannot%20be%20influenced%20to%20suit%20its%20needs%20the%20way%20an%20election%20can.%20International%20umpires%20are%20not%20the%20Indian%20judiciary.%20The%20ICC%20is%20not%20(yet)%20the%20Indian%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20India%20lost%20in%20the%20final%20was%20karmic%20payback%20for%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20sins%20against%20the%20game%2C%20and%20also%20for%20the%20Ahmedabad%20crowd%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20be%20sporting%20and%20civilised%2C%20to%20appreciate%20cricket%20as%20something%20other%20than%20a%20jingoistic%20exercise%20in%20which%20India%20must%20win%20every%20game%20to%20the%20chanting%20of%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%E2%80%9D.%20Let%20us%20never%20again%20hold%20the%20final%20of%20a%20World%20Cup%20in%20such%20a%20city%2C%20a%20place%20in%20which%20cricket%20is%20but%20the%20means%20to%20petty%20nationalist%20ends%2C%20where%20few%20stand%20up%20to%20applaud%20an%20opposing%20batsman%20who%20scores%20a%20magnificent%2C%20match-winning%20hundred.%20Stay%20with%20Chennai%2C%20with%20Mumbai%2C%20with%20Kolkata%2C%20where%20the%20crowds%20love%20cricket%20(and%20not%20just%20winning).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hush%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20Pleased%20Cummins%20but%20it%20Diminished%20India%20in%20the%20Eyes%20of%20the%20World%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-pradeep-magazine%5C%22%3EHush%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20Pleased%20Cummins%20but%20it%20Diminished%20India%20in%20the%20Eyes%20of%20the%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20justice%20was%20done.%20Australia%20won.%20Narendra%20Modi%20did%20not%20get%20his%20heavily%20scripted%20opportunity%20to%20strut%20on%20stage%20at%20the%20stadium%20named%20after%20him.%20Instead%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20most%20graceless%20presentation%20of%20a%20cup%20to%20a%20winning%20captain%2C%20in%20which%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20sulking%20like%20a%20spoiled%20child%20who%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20had%20the%20celebration%20he%E2%80%99d%20thought%20was%20his%20birthright%20%E2%80%93%20handed%20over%20the%20trophy%20to%20Pat%20Cummins%20and%20then%20turned%20his%20back%20on%20the%20Australian%20captain.%20The%20latter%20was%20left%20bemused%20and%20sheepish%20on%20the%20stage%2C%20alone%20with%20the%20cup%20that%20his%20team%20had%20won%20but%20feeling%2C%20nonetheless%2C%20like%20a%20gate-crasher%20at%20a%20party-gone-wrong.%20For%20India%2C%20it%20was%20a%20moment%20of%20national%20embarrassment.%20The%20prime%20minister%20had%20reduced%20an%20ancient%20land%20to%20a%20boorish%20place%2C%20ill-mannered%2C%20inhospitable%2C%20uncivilised%2C%20nouveau-riche.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20give%20thanks%20to%20the%20God%20of%20Cricket%20that%20the%20BCCI%20lost%20on%20Sunday%2C%20even%20as%20we%20embrace%20our%20gallant%20boys%20in%20blue.%20Maybe%20some%20of%20them%20will%20be%20emboldened%20now%20to%20push%20back%20against%20the%20BCCI%20in%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeat%20after%20me%3A%20Cricket%20Mata%20ki%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETunku%20Varadarajan%20is%20a%20writer%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3Cem%3E%20in%20New%20York.%20A%20fellow%20at%20the%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute%2C%20he%20is%20also%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20Classical%20Liberal%20Institute%20at%20New%20York%20University%20Law%20School.%20He%20has%20written%20frequently%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3EWisden%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700532043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20234455%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-11.44.17-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-mata-ki-jai-jingoism-lost-in-ahmedabad-on-sunday%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22That%20India%20lost%20in%20the%20final%20was%20karmic%20payback%20for%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20sins%20against%20the%20game%2C%20and%20also%20for%20the%20Ahmedabad%20crowd%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20be%20sporting%20and%20civilised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-mata-ki-jai-jingoism-lost-in-ahmedabad