sferred%20to%20the%20T.D.P.%20party%E2%80%99s%20account.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20Naidu%20could%20not%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20all%20the%20discrepancies%20noted%20in%20the%20forensic%20audit%20report%20as%20per%20which%20out%20of%20the%20Rs%20371%20crore%2C%20at%20least%20Rs%20241%20crore%20were%20misappropriated%20by%20SISW%20and%20Design%20Tech%20and%20diverted%20to%20various%20shell%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Prosecution%20needs%20to%20clarify%20how%20the%20petitioner%20can%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20such%20discrepancies%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20his%20duty%2C%20as%20the%20then%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20to%20verify%20and%20compare%20parties%E2%80%99%20signatures%E2%80%A6It%20remains%20to%20be%20clarified%20how%20the%20differences%20outlined%20in%20the%20report%20can%20be%20deemed%20the%20fundamental%20cause%20for%20the%20alleged%20misappropriation%20of%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20October%2031%2C%20the%20court%20had%20granted%20Naidu%20four%20weeks%E2%80%99%20medical%20bail.%20He%20had%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20CID%20on%20September%209%20and%20has%20been%20in%20the%20Rajahmundry%20central%20prison%20since%20September%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CID%20has%20listed%20Naidu%20as%20%E2%80%98accused%20number%20one%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20alleged%20skill%20development%20scam.%20He%20is%20charged%20with%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20cheating%2C%20forgery%2C%20breach%20of%20trust%2C%20destruction%20of%20evidence%2C%20and%20abetment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20reported%20that%20the%20scam%20is%20allegedly%20a%20Rs%20279-crore%20one.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fandhrapradesh%2Fap-cid-chief-n-sanjay-seems-to-have-a-penchant-for-prosecuting-chandrababu-naidu-and-his-relatives%2F%5C%22%3Enews%20outlet%20has%20also%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20CID%20chief%20N%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20run-ins%20with%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20kin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%20leaders%20Kaluva%20Srinivasulu%2C%20Bhuma%20Brahmananda%20Reddy%2C%20A.V.%20Subba%20Reddy%2C%20B.C.%20Janardhan%20Reddy%20and%20Akhila%20Priya%20were%20also%20arrested%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20has%20claimed%20that%20this%20case%20is%20an%20act%20of%20political%20vendetta%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700496198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24143246%2Fnaidu.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fandhra-pradesh-hc-gives-n-chandrababu-naidu-bail-in-skill-development-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20judge%20said%20it%20cannot%20be%20definitively%20concluded%20that%20the%20misappropriated%20amounts%20were%20diverted%20to%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party's%20bank%20accounts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fandhra-pradesh-hc-gives-n-chandrababu-naidu-bail-in-skill-development-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CONCOR%20ties%20up%20Indraprastha%20Gas%20to%20explore%20possibility%20of%20LNG%20infra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700495464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2018-10%2F02%2Ffull%2F1538473969-017.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fconcor-ties-up-indraprastha-gas-to-explore-possibility-of-lng-infra-123112001084_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CONCOR%20and%20IGL%20also%20agree%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20transportation%20of%20LNG%20in%20future%20through%20railway%20rakes%20from%20LNG%20terminals%20near%20sea%20ports%20like%20Dahej%20in%20Gujarat%20to%20desired%20locations%20within%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonica