%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202016%20when%20he%20met%20an%20Australian%20man%20who%20had%20settled%20in%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20spent%20some%20time%20in%20Alaska%20and%20knew%20the%20way%20an%20Igloo%20is%20made.%20He%20gave%20us%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20the%20science%20behind%20the%20construction%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFurthermore%2C%20we%20used%20the%20internet%20extensively%20to%20understand%20the%20process.%20I%20also%20used%20YouTube%20to%20see%20how%20people%20live%20in%20them%20and%20how%20sustainable%20they%20are%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20climate%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334307%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVinod%20has%20hosted%20hundreds%20of%20guests%20at%20his%20igloos.%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20Vinod%20Bodh%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202017%2C%20the%20Igloos%20were%20up%20and%20ready%20to%20use.%20%E2%80%9CI%20named%20them%20Igloo%20Sethan%20Village%20because%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20a%20tribute%20to%20my%20childhood%20summer%20home%20and%20a%20tribute%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELive%20like%20the%20eskimos%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20initial%20reaction%20of%20the%20people%2C%20Vinod%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20elated.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20fascination%20with%20snow%2C%20and%20they%20responded%20very%20well%20to%20the%20Igloos.%20Of%20course%2C%20they%20had%20a%20few%20doubts%2C%20and%20some%20would%20ask%20me%20if%20it%20would%20fall.%20I%20would%20sometimes%20explain%20to%20them%20the%20construction%20process%20to%20assure%20them%20that%20they%20are%20safe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20process%20of%20making%20an%20Igloo%2C%20Vinod%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20time%2C%20construction%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Igloo%2C%20it%20all%20depends%20on%20the%20ice.%20The%20snow%20that%20falls%20in%20December%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334115%2Fbest-homestays-in-himachal-pradesh-uttarakhand-to-enjoy-snowfall-in-winter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowder%20snow%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it%20does%20not%20stick%20easily.%20We%20have%20to%20water%20it%20to%20make%20it%20stick%20and%20it%20takes%20longer%20for%20us%20to%20make%20the%20Igloo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20snow%20in%20the%20later%20days%20is%20thicker%20and%20more%20stable%2C%20it%20only%20takes%20a%20day%20to%20complete%20the%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20shape%20of%20the%20Igloo%20is%20oval%20because%20it%20distributes%20the%20weight%20into%20equal%20parts.%20As%20the%