d%20the%20restaurant%20by%20using%20their%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20recipes%20and%20recreating%20delicacies%20from%20South%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Suhas%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20been%20full%20of%20learning%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20feels%20immensely%20contented.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20retire%20to%20my%20bed%2C%20I%20sleep%20peacefully%20knowing%20the%20value%20of%20the%20work%20I%20do.%20With%20this%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20revive%20my%20native%20delicacies%20in%20the%20simplest%20form%20with%20high%20nutritional%20value%20%E2%80%94%20just%20the%20way%20my%20grandma%20offered%20it%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Jagli%20Tindi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700141878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fjagli-tindi-1-1700140193.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Craving%20Mangalore%20buns%2C%20mandakki%20upkari%20and%20khotte%20kadabu%3F%20Bengaluru-based%20couple%20Suhas%20Karanth%20and%20Raksha%20Prasad%20are%20recreating%20the%20authentic%20food%20of%20Karnataka's%20Dakshina%20Kannada%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334273%2Fbengaluru-couple-recreate-traditional-dakshina-kannada-food-entrepreneurs-karnataka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20Purifier%20to%20Amplifier%3A%205%20Clay%20Innovations%20Harnessing%20the%20Immense%20Potential%20of%20Terracotta%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagination%20and%20creativity%20knows%20no%20bounds.%20Innovators%20have%20shown%20us%20that%20with%20out-of-the-box%20thinking%2C%20anything%20is%20possible.%20Clay%20has%20traditionally%20been%20used%20to%20keep%20water%20cool.%20When%20it%20keeps%20water%20cool%2C%20can%20it